Title: Cecilia
Writer: Jorge Ramos, Nelson Rodríguez, Humberto Solás, Norma Torrado, Cirilo Villaverde (novel)
Actors: Daisy Granados, Imanol Arias, Raquel Revuelta, Miguel Benavides
Plot: In 1830s Havana, amidst the Cuban independence movement, social climber Cecilia Valdés uses santería to conquer Leonardo Gamboa, the son of a rich colonialist family.
